16Neh 11:32 Anathoth, Nob, Ananiah,
16Neh 11:33 Hazor, Ramah, Gittaim,
16Neh 11:34 Hadid, Zeboim, Neballat,
16Neh 11:35 Lod, and Ono, the valley of craftsmen.
