16Neh 12:1 These are the priests and the Levites who came up with Zerubbabel the son of Shealtiel, and Jeshua: Seraiah, Jeremiah, Ezra,
16Neh 12:2 Amariah, Malluch, Hattush,
16Neh 12:3 Shecaniah, Rehum, Meremoth,
16Neh 12:4 Iddo, Ginnethoi, Abijah,
16Neh 12:5 Mijamin, Maadiah, Bilgah,
16Neh 12:6 Shemaiah, Joiarib, Jedaiah,
16Neh 12:7 Sallu, Amok, Hilkiah, Jedaiah. These were the chiefs of the priests and of their brothers in the days of Jeshua.
16Neh 12:8 And the Levites: Jeshua, Binnui, Kadmiel, Sherebiah, Judah, and Mattaniah, who with his brothers was in charge of the songs of thanksgiving.
16Neh 12:9 And Bakbukiah and Unni and their brothers stood opposite them in the service.
16Neh 12:10 And Jeshua was the father of Joiakim, Joiakim the father of Eliashib, Eliashib the father of Joiada,
16Neh 12:11 Joiada the father of Jonathan, and Jonathan the father of Jaddua.
